    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Wherever your plans may take you, our soft fleece throw blanket is the perfect fleece throw blanket to keep you warm indoors or outdoors<BR><BR>Incredibly soft, warm and cozy, these plush throw blankets from ASR Outdoor have a design that boast traditional southwestern flair with a nod to classic and timeless Navajo and Aztec inspired design. The fleece blankets are ultra soft, as well as insulating, making them a great item to include with your hiking or camping gear, but also entirely suitable for movie marathon nights in, as a beach or picnic blanket or for an evening of summer stargazing</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n<head>\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-repeat: repeat-x;\n\t\t\tborder-radius: 4px;\n\t\t\t-webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255,